WEBVTT

01:39.530 --> 01:43.930
[Road to Success]

01:46.590 --> 01:48.780
♪ And water the seeds ♪

01:49.460 --> 01:52.220
♪ Let the good times glow ♪

01:54.580 --> 01:56.390
♪ And water seeds ♪

01:56.840 --> 01:59.140
♪ Let the good time ♪

02:00.030 --> 02:03.190
♪ Let the good time flow ♪

02:04.430 --> 02:06.480
If you withdraw from school now,

02:06.480 --> 02:08.039
you can still save the last bit of dignity

02:06.890 --> 02:07.890
[Withdrawal Application]

02:08.039 --> 02:09.840
for yourself and Professor Shu.

02:12.980 --> 02:15.550
[Goodbye, My Love]

02:13.000 --> 02:14.560
Professor Shu was such a good person,

02:14.560 --> 02:15.680
and he died because of her.

02:15.680 --> 02:16.680
To get a PhD,

02:16.680 --> 02:17.750
you knowingly became a mistress.

02:17.750 --> 02:18.560
Shameless.

02:20.000 --> 02:21.960
If you don't want your teacher

02:21.960 --> 02:23.360
to be criticized after death,

02:23.360 --> 02:24.620
withdraw from school.

02:30.400 --> 02:31.560
Heads,

02:32.310 --> 02:33.310
I go ahead;

02:34.280 --> 02:35.190
tails,

02:35.960 --> 02:36.910
I stay.

03:05.000 --> 03:06.000
Wanxing.

03:06.280 --> 03:08.000
A person's life

03:08.000 --> 03:09.670
is like a stream,

03:09.870 --> 03:11.840
only flowing forward.

03:12.150 --> 03:14.110
You can look back,

03:14.240 --> 03:16.470
but you cannot go back,

03:16.720 --> 03:20.200
because life itself is ahead.

03:20.320 --> 03:23.750
If you haven't seen the path ahead yet,

03:24.030 --> 03:27.270
I suggest that you
come to Hongjing No. 8 High School.

03:27.520 --> 03:30.470
School is a healing place.

03:28.390 --> 03:32.320
[Grandpa, who loves you forever]

03:31.079 --> 03:33.070
Go find yourself.

03:58.180 --> 04:05.920
[Hongjing]

04:04.360 --> 04:05.310
We are now arriving at

04:05.310 --> 04:06.400
Hongjing Station.

04:07.240 --> 04:10.680
[Episode 1]

04:11.860 --> 04:19.370
[Three months later]

04:40.390 --> 04:41.390
Grandpa,

04:41.720 --> 04:43.240
I've decided to listen to you

04:43.240 --> 04:44.800
and start over.

04:45.750 --> 04:46.950
This time,

04:47.420 --> 04:49.620
I want to look forward in a different way

04:49.730 --> 04:53.580
and live a carefree life.

05:23.230 --> 05:24.030
Grandpa,

05:24.830 --> 05:27.630
I'm reporting
to Hongjing No. 8 High School today.

05:27.870 --> 05:29.930
Although I'm just a contract worker,

05:30.050 --> 05:31.780
I'll work hard to keep this job.

05:35.530 --> 05:36.440
Don't worry.

05:37.150 --> 05:38.390
I'll be fine.

05:39.180 --> 05:39.900
Bye.

05:58.640 --> 05:59.700
Morning, Mr. Kang.

05:59.720 --> 06:00.870
Morning, Wanxing.

06:02.340 --> 06:04.950
[Hongjing No. 8 High School]

06:07.190 --> 06:08.450
Coming back to the place
where my grandparents

06:08.450 --> 06:09.840
used to work and live,

06:10.250 --> 06:12.250
it suddenly gives me a warm feeling.

06:12.950 --> 06:13.780
It's simple

06:14.510 --> 06:15.510
and peaceful.

06:22.680 --> 06:24.080
Lin Wanxing,

06:24.410 --> 06:26.470
since you've decided to be a slacker,

06:27.000 --> 06:28.640
just start now

06:29.040 --> 06:30.480
and enjoy it.

06:30.710 --> 06:34.260
[P.E. Department Office]

06:34.430 --> 06:40.370
[Teacher Employment Registration Form]

06:34.830 --> 06:36.360
Lin Wanxing.

06:37.150 --> 06:40.510
Department of Psychology,
Yongchuan University...

06:40.750 --> 06:41.540
Ph.D?

06:41.760 --> 06:42.580
I dropped out.

06:42.620 --> 06:44.130
That's still impressive.

06:44.720 --> 06:45.930
Academic achievements.

06:45.930 --> 06:47.460
[Work-Related Academic Achievements]

06:46.680 --> 06:49.080
I currently have no academic achievements

06:49.120 --> 06:50.250
related to this job.

06:52.070 --> 06:54.070
With such a high degree as a Ph.D.,

06:55.070 --> 06:56.000
Ms. Lin,

06:56.480 --> 06:59.420
why do you want to be
a sports equipment manager

06:59.550 --> 07:01.110
at our school?

07:01.560 --> 07:03.430
I think this job is quite relaxed.

07:11.110 --> 07:12.580
No matter what the position is,

07:12.580 --> 07:14.640
it's all contributing to education.

07:16.200 --> 07:17.100
The equipment room

07:17.100 --> 07:18.630
is right by the playground.

07:19.190 --> 07:19.920
Follow me.

07:23.000 --> 07:24.330
This is the smaller one.

07:25.230 --> 07:26.600
Take a look.

07:26.950 --> 07:28.480
The bigger one is over here.

07:28.940 --> 07:32.070
[Sports Equipment Room]

07:34.600 --> 07:35.430
Come on in.

07:37.630 --> 07:38.750
The room is a bit messy.

07:38.750 --> 07:40.810
No one has been in here for a long time.

07:41.600 --> 07:42.300
Be careful.

07:43.390 --> 07:44.600
Well,

07:44.750 --> 07:46.280
the environment is not bad.

07:46.500 --> 07:47.420
Ms. Lin,

07:47.480 --> 07:48.600
this is your desk.

07:53.440 --> 07:54.600
Next,

07:54.630 --> 07:56.020
I'll brief you on how things work

07:56.020 --> 07:57.600
in this storage room.

07:58.159 --> 07:58.950
Take some notes.

07:58.950 --> 07:59.270
Okay.

07:59.270 --> 08:00.070
Look.

08:00.200 --> 08:02.280
All balls need to be organized.

08:02.310 --> 08:03.840
For example,

08:03.860 --> 08:04.920
these basketballs

08:04.950 --> 08:05.750
and soccer balls

08:05.750 --> 08:07.410
must be placed in this basket.

08:07.440 --> 08:09.800
Tennis rackets
need to be hung on the wall.

08:09.820 --> 08:11.390
Don't put all the basketballs together.

08:11.390 --> 08:12.610
Put them in different boxes.

08:12.610 --> 08:14.750
-Okay, Director Qian.
-Keep the balls together and the rackets together.

08:14.750 --> 08:15.270
These boxes

08:15.270 --> 08:16.190
are probably empty.

08:16.190 --> 08:18.040
Put the shuttlecocks in them

08:18.040 --> 08:18.560
one by one.

08:18.560 --> 08:19.230
Look at this.

08:19.230 --> 08:19.950
It's a total mess.

08:19.950 --> 08:21.720
Why is this pommel horse missing a leg?

08:21.720 --> 08:22.720
The leg is over there.

08:22.720 --> 08:23.830
Reattach it later.

08:24.310 --> 08:25.640
Stack the trampolines.

08:25.640 --> 08:27.050
Stack them neatly.

08:28.300 --> 08:29.850
It's actually not too complicated.

08:29.850 --> 08:31.000
It mainly requires

08:31.270 --> 08:32.559
patience and care.

08:32.580 --> 08:33.470
Oh, right.

08:33.500 --> 08:34.960
One more important thing.

08:35.070 --> 08:36.190
No equipment

08:36.190 --> 08:37.390
can be borrowed

08:37.390 --> 08:38.600
without a teacher's permission.

08:38.600 --> 08:39.809
Even if borrowed,

08:40.490 --> 08:42.419
they must be returned the same day.

08:42.600 --> 08:43.270
Noted.

08:43.270 --> 08:44.870
All equipment needs
a teacher's approval to be borrowed

08:44.870 --> 08:45.960
and must be returned the same day.

08:45.960 --> 08:46.850
The probation period

08:46.850 --> 08:47.580
is one month.

08:47.720 --> 08:49.750
There's a PE department meeting tomorrow.

08:49.750 --> 08:50.840
You must attend.

08:50.840 --> 08:53.320
Meeting attendance is counted
towards your evaluation.

08:53.320 --> 08:54.390
Don't worry, Director Qian.

08:54.390 --> 08:56.320
I will definitely take the initiative

08:56.320 --> 08:59.080
and accomplish
this glorious and arduous task.

08:59.320 --> 09:00.320
Here are the keys.

09:02.350 --> 09:03.350
I'll be going now.

09:03.530 --> 09:04.410
Thank you.

09:07.200 --> 09:08.960
He's finally done talking.

09:15.510 --> 09:16.420
It's so dirty.

09:16.990 --> 09:18.630
It needs a good cleaning.

09:19.990 --> 09:23.060
[Knowledge is Boundless]

09:42.880 --> 09:45.540
[Chen Jianghe,
Former Football Team Forward]

09:44.090 --> 09:45.420
The door wasn't locked?

09:55.640 --> 09:56.780
Why don't you...

09:57.780 --> 09:58.920
come down first?

10:07.960 --> 10:08.840
So,

10:09.200 --> 10:10.960
why did you climb in through the window?

10:10.960 --> 10:12.290
What are you doing here?

10:12.320 --> 10:13.320
Cleaning up.

10:14.670 --> 10:15.910
Then clean it well.

10:15.930 --> 10:17.860
And don't forget to close the door.

10:22.030 --> 10:22.910
Hey.

10:25.880 --> 10:26.690
What?

10:26.720 --> 10:28.270
Don't you need to get a teacher's

10:28.270 --> 10:29.650
permission to borrow a football?

10:29.650 --> 10:31.120
What does that have to do with you?

10:31.120 --> 10:33.670
You got cleaning duty
for not wearing your school uniform,

10:33.670 --> 10:36.070
and now you want to snitch on me
to a teacher?

10:37.200 --> 10:39.080
I don't need to snitch on you
to a teacher.

10:39.080 --> 10:40.320
Then what do you want?

10:40.390 --> 10:41.750
I want to tell you

10:42.320 --> 10:43.600
that I am a teacher.

10:48.520 --> 10:50.320
Are... are you really a teacher?

10:51.320 --> 10:52.440
I'm new here.

10:52.590 --> 10:54.650
I'm in charge of this equipment room.

10:54.840 --> 10:56.790
Since you're a teacher,

10:56.790 --> 10:58.550
why were you acting so sneaky just now

10:58.550 --> 10:59.750
and not locking the door?

10:59.750 --> 11:01.670
Who was the one being sneaky?

11:06.980 --> 11:08.530
You are in charge of the sports equipment?

11:08.530 --> 11:09.370
Well...

11:09.390 --> 11:10.600
what sport are you in, teacher?

11:10.600 --> 11:11.440
Weightlifting.

11:11.440 --> 11:12.550
Are you kidding me?

11:12.550 --> 11:13.600
Glad you know.

11:16.390 --> 11:18.120
What grade and class are you in?

11:18.510 --> 11:19.550
What's your name?

11:21.820 --> 11:22.920
I'm a senior in Class 5.

11:22.920 --> 11:23.850
My name is Qin Ao.

11:24.320 --> 11:25.440
Qin as in Emperor Qin.

11:25.440 --> 11:26.390
Ao as in Tibetan Mastiff,

11:26.390 --> 11:28.050
without the "dog" component.

11:32.180 --> 11:33.870
Which teacher sent you?

11:33.890 --> 11:35.060
You're so annoying.

11:35.710 --> 11:37.040
Then don't lend it to me.

11:53.320 --> 11:54.200
Does this work?

11:55.920 --> 12:00.300
[100 free football equipment rentals]

12:04.400 --> 12:05.240
Just this?

12:06.230 --> 12:07.740
I knew I got tricked.

12:07.770 --> 12:08.870
This works too.

12:09.110 --> 12:10.370
I'll lend you the ball.

12:10.420 --> 12:11.830
What... did you say?

12:11.850 --> 12:13.000
I said,

12:13.030 --> 12:14.070
this works.

12:14.410 --> 12:15.200
Really?

12:15.870 --> 12:17.070
Then who will sign it?

12:20.880 --> 12:22.120
But on one condition.

12:22.140 --> 12:24.300
Come help clean up during the break.

12:25.200 --> 12:27.120
You must return the ball today.

12:27.370 --> 12:28.090
Take it.

12:30.290 --> 12:33.530
Climbing the window
instead of using the door?

12:33.630 --> 12:36.020
The students here
surely have some personality.

12:36.020 --> 12:38.170
A 100-use ball borrowing card?

12:38.750 --> 12:40.280
Interesting.

12:46.850 --> 12:49.570
Having other students do the work for you?

12:51.370 --> 12:52.620
[Sports Equipment Check-Out/Return Form]

12:51.720 --> 12:54.840
Mr. Tibetan Mastiff,

12:52.620 --> 12:55.930
[100 free football equipment rentals]

12:57.450 --> 13:00.220
you have failed my trust.

13:00.250 --> 13:01.300
Hey.

13:01.330 --> 13:03.730
Remember to lock the door
when you're done.

13:04.470 --> 13:05.470
This is a bad deal.

13:05.790 --> 13:06.790
Chen Jianghe is playing football,

13:06.790 --> 13:08.390
making us do the work for him.

13:09.150 --> 13:11.820
[Grade 12 Class 5]

13:10.910 --> 13:14.160
I'm going to clean house today!

13:14.670 --> 13:15.600
Young Master!

13:15.600 --> 13:17.380
I've been so loyal to you!

13:19.310 --> 13:23.670
[Qin Ao, Former Football Team Forward]

13:23.910 --> 13:24.840
Young Heroine.

13:24.840 --> 13:25.600
Trying so hard?

13:25.600 --> 13:26.360
I've been poisoned.

13:26.360 --> 13:27.780
-Please help me.
-Master Qin Ao.

13:27.780 --> 13:29.640
Aren't you a martial arts master?

13:29.910 --> 13:30.790
Do it yourself.

13:31.640 --> 13:34.550
Boss, you were a bit overconfident.

13:34.910 --> 13:35.840
Let's go.

13:35.840 --> 13:36.640
Bao Xiaotian,

13:36.740 --> 13:38.070
tomorrow morning...

13:38.090 --> 13:38.960
I'll have Xiaolongbao for breakfast.

13:38.960 --> 13:40.090
I'll bring you some.

13:40.120 --> 13:41.130
Let's go, Yu Ming!

13:45.840 --> 13:46.720
Excuse me,

13:47.000 --> 13:48.390
is Qin Ao here?

13:48.020 --> 13:48.840
[Lin Lu, Former Football Team Defender]
[Yu Ming, Former Football Team Defender]

13:48.860 --> 13:49.500
[Qin Ao, Former Football Team Forward]

13:49.630 --> 13:50.690
She's here for you?

13:52.320 --> 13:53.030
Beautiful,

13:53.240 --> 13:54.440
do we know each other?

13:54.600 --> 13:55.530
What do you want?

13:56.360 --> 13:57.480
Just as I thought.

13:58.270 --> 13:59.390
What?

13:59.440 --> 14:01.670
When someone is introducing themselves,

14:01.670 --> 14:03.200
they wouldn't say something like

14:03.200 --> 14:04.860
"without the dog component".

14:06.030 --> 14:07.150
Today, a student with a buzz cut

14:07.150 --> 14:08.610
came to the equipment room

14:08.840 --> 14:10.030
and borrowed a football from me

14:10.030 --> 14:11.840
with this football lending card.

14:11.840 --> 14:12.790
He said

14:12.960 --> 14:14.340
his name is Qin Ao.

14:15.320 --> 14:16.720
That Chen Jianghe! He...

14:17.550 --> 14:18.480
He must've skipped class again

14:18.480 --> 14:20.080
and snuck off campus to play football.

14:20.080 --> 14:20.600
Don't be angry.

14:20.600 --> 14:21.070
Boss, let's go.

14:21.070 --> 14:22.600
I'll treat you to some meatballs.

14:22.600 --> 14:25.440
Chen-Jiang-He.

14:29.480 --> 14:30.840
Great ball! Great ball!

14:30.840 --> 14:31.600
Let's go!

14:32.960 --> 14:34.600
It's fine! Great ball!

14:34.600 --> 14:35.960
Don't rush!

14:35.960 --> 14:37.470
Pass it back! Pass it back!

14:37.720 --> 14:38.600
Good ball!

14:39.320 --> 14:40.440
Pass it back!

14:40.440 --> 14:41.440
Good ball!

14:44.320 --> 14:46.390
-Move up!
-Pass it!

14:46.390 --> 14:47.030
Over here!

14:48.080 --> 14:48.960
Good shot!

14:51.670 --> 14:52.840
-Nice!
-Nice!

14:52.840 --> 14:54.840
Good shot!

14:56.440 --> 14:58.030
Defense!

14:58.030 --> 14:59.440
Watch the ball!

15:04.320 --> 15:05.200
Let's go!

15:06.930 --> 15:09.060
♪ Two souls alike ♪

15:10.800 --> 15:12.680
♪ In the silent gravity ♪

15:14.960 --> 15:16.890
♪ Cure my heart ♪

15:17.710 --> 15:20.320
♪ With every part of you ♪

15:22.860 --> 15:24.820
♪ Our words flow ♪

15:25.320 --> 15:26.120
It's her.

15:26.340 --> 15:28.570
♪ Like a gentle stream ♪

15:30.660 --> 15:32.840
♪ They glow like fireflies ♪

15:33.500 --> 15:36.020
♪ Inside of a silky dream ♪

15:38.230 --> 15:44.060
♪ We talked the whole night, breeze away ♪

15:46.040 --> 15:47.830
♪ Together we set out on a long journey ♪

15:48.460 --> 15:51.520
♪ The endless journey ♪

15:54.230 --> 15:57.700
♪ Gently smoothing away ♪

15:58.430 --> 16:03.120
♪ The hesitation in each other's eyes ♪

16:02.600 --> 16:03.460
Help yourself.

16:04.150 --> 16:08.230
♪ Hearing the warmth inside ♪

16:09.910 --> 16:12.100
♪ Life begins alone ♪

16:13.030 --> 16:15.770
♪ A road we walk alone ♪

16:17.640 --> 16:19.930
♪ Until fate brings warmth ♪

16:19.550 --> 16:20.100
Thanks.

16:20.640 --> 16:23.040
♪ To light our way back home ♪

16:21.840 --> 16:23.150
-Good ball!
-Beautiful!

16:23.150 --> 16:23.790
Go!

16:24.270 --> 16:25.270
Pass the ball now!

16:25.790 --> 16:27.120
-Nice! Nice!
-Bring it inside!

16:27.120 --> 16:28.240
Don't rush!

16:28.480 --> 16:30.340
Didn't you tell me to help myself?

16:31.790 --> 16:32.840
I meant,

16:33.150 --> 16:34.950
I'd just share a little with you.

16:36.750 --> 16:37.750
Move!

16:37.750 --> 16:38.720
Pass it!

16:38.720 --> 16:39.390
Over here!

16:40.320 --> 16:41.030
You know what?

16:41.030 --> 16:41.720
Here, here!

16:41.960 --> 16:42.750
That boy

16:42.750 --> 16:44.790
has been playing football there
all afternoon.

16:44.790 --> 16:45.640
He must be skipping class.

16:45.640 --> 16:46.240
Hey, kid.

16:46.320 --> 16:46.960
Hold on.

16:47.240 --> 16:48.240
What's your name?

16:49.000 --> 16:50.200
That man is a scammer.

16:50.390 --> 16:53.200
-You seem to be the only teacher around here.
-I'm a scout for a football club.

16:53.200 --> 16:54.670
I think you've got a lot of potential.

16:54.670 --> 16:56.510
-This scammer is a pro.
-You can register with our team.

16:56.510 --> 16:59.090
-If he can't get him, he'll scam him out of his money.
-If you join our team—I'm telling you...

16:59.090 --> 17:00.510
-For example, personal loans.
-Our club

17:00.510 --> 17:04.910
-ruining their families or something.
-will give you professional training.

17:06.960 --> 17:08.550
This isn't part of my job.

17:11.790 --> 17:12.859
Just sign this.

17:13.030 --> 17:14.069
Bro, sign here.

17:14.069 --> 17:14.880
Wait a minute.

17:15.440 --> 17:15.960
Who...

17:15.960 --> 17:17.030
Who are you?

17:18.589 --> 17:19.480
I'm his sister.

17:20.829 --> 17:21.960
My surname is Liu.

17:21.960 --> 17:22.960
I'm with Yongchuan Hengjiu,

17:22.960 --> 17:24.589
a professional scout
for their youth academy.

17:24.589 --> 17:26.829
Your brother is a football genius.

17:27.440 --> 17:28.960
I've been keeping an eye on him
for a while.

17:28.960 --> 17:30.200
My advice is

17:30.200 --> 17:31.590
that he take a year off from school,

17:31.590 --> 17:32.960
play for our club,

17:32.960 --> 17:34.310
and become a star in the future.

17:34.310 --> 17:35.720
As long as he joins our team,

17:35.720 --> 17:38.590
he'll definitely have a chance
to play in a professional league.

17:38.590 --> 17:40.480
Does your club charge a fee?

17:41.790 --> 17:43.720
The 3-month training fee is 10,000 yuan.

17:43.720 --> 17:44.790
That's not much.

17:44.790 --> 17:46.390
Most families can afford it.

17:49.270 --> 17:50.000
How about it?

17:50.720 --> 17:52.920
If you're interested, we can talk more.

17:53.300 --> 17:55.130
Since your club is so good,

17:55.160 --> 17:56.400
I should tell the school

17:56.400 --> 17:57.860
and ask them to promote it.

17:57.960 --> 17:58.440
Wait a moment.

17:58.440 --> 17:59.200
I'll go get my phone.

17:59.200 --> 17:59.920
No, no, no.

18:00.550 --> 18:02.110
I have a meeting this afternoon.

18:02.110 --> 18:02.920
I'll contact you later.

18:02.920 --> 18:04.250
I'll contact you later.

18:04.830 --> 18:05.750
Well...

18:05.750 --> 18:06.890
Give me my pen.

18:06.910 --> 18:07.910
We'll be in touch.

18:09.680 --> 18:10.550
Scammers nowadays

18:10.550 --> 18:11.920
are too blatant.

18:12.620 --> 18:13.540
Are you crazy?

18:14.550 --> 18:16.070
You think I didn't know he was a scammer?

18:16.070 --> 18:18.000
Don't I know what I'm capable of?

18:18.920 --> 18:21.780
Do you think youth training
is about who's the best?

18:22.110 --> 18:24.370
It's about who bribes the coach
the most.

18:26.080 --> 18:27.740
Being a professional player?

18:28.160 --> 18:30.020
I've never had that kind of dream.

18:30.880 --> 18:31.400
Wait a minute.

18:31.400 --> 18:32.600
What else do you want?

18:34.160 --> 18:35.200
Return the ball.

18:35.830 --> 18:39.310
Chen-Jiang-He.

18:42.440 --> 18:43.440
Stop right there!

18:50.200 --> 18:52.110
Director Qian, you're here?

19:05.110 --> 19:06.830
♪ Every night ♪

19:07.590 --> 19:09.810
♪ I reach out to touch the starlight ♪

19:10.680 --> 19:12.610
♪ Wandering through dreams with you ♪

19:13.410 --> 19:15.570
♪ I follow the beat of my heart ♪

19:16.380 --> 19:18.930
♪ Like dust floating in the air ♪

19:18.350 --> 19:19.790
Thank you for watching my bag.

19:19.690 --> 19:21.720
♪ Because of your love ♪

19:20.270 --> 19:21.200
You're welcome.

19:22.540 --> 19:27.340
♪ I shine brilliantly ♪

19:24.160 --> 19:25.500
How did you know I'm a teacher?

19:25.500 --> 19:26.370
Do we know each other?

19:26.370 --> 19:27.080
No.

19:28.310 --> 19:28.920
But...

19:29.110 --> 19:30.030
we do now.

19:30.600 --> 19:31.220
[Receive Money by QR Code]

19:32.660 --> 19:33.490
Sorry.

19:33.510 --> 19:35.710
I don't just add anyone on WeChat.

19:35.820 --> 19:37.750
[Receive Money by QR Code]

19:39.310 --> 19:40.550
[Receive Money by QR Code]

19:43.240 --> 19:44.440
Why are you asking me for money?

19:44.440 --> 19:45.310
Storage fee.

19:48.790 --> 19:50.680
♪ I caught your eyes ♪

19:51.330 --> 19:53.700
♪ On the summer night ♪

19:51.930 --> 19:52.350
[Receive Money by QR Code]

19:52.370 --> 19:52.800
[Pay to Individuals]

19:54.190 --> 19:59.380
♪ A star that glows so bright ♪

19:59.480 --> 20:00.640
What a day.

20:00.640 --> 20:02.640
What kind of people
have I been running into?

20:01.220 --> 20:03.480
♪ A spark in my heart ♪

20:02.660 --> 20:04.940
Charging a storage fee
just for watching a bag?

20:04.180 --> 20:09.670
♪ Disappear in my dream, secretly ♪

20:22.920 --> 20:24.070
Mom.

20:24.070 --> 20:25.590
I'll help you carry this.

20:25.590 --> 20:26.550
Thank you.

20:26.550 --> 20:27.750
You're welcome.

20:27.750 --> 20:28.920
Do you like our new house?

20:28.920 --> 20:30.070
I do.

20:30.550 --> 20:32.000
You can make new friends tomorrow.

20:32.000 --> 20:35.600
-The new tenants moved in so quickly?
-Okay. I'm so happy to move.

21:12.700 --> 21:14.440
[One and a Half Years Ago, UK]

21:13.990 --> 21:16.100
Jason, don't rush! Wait for me!

21:25.440 --> 21:27.790
I entrusted my child to you.

21:28.480 --> 21:31.590
Did you really take good care of him?

21:32.550 --> 21:33.270
I'm sorry.

21:40.970 --> 21:41.170
[Are you going back to China
after graduation?]

21:41.200 --> 21:41.580
[Thank you. In the UK,]

21:41.600 --> 21:41.910
[you're the first friend
to send me a gift.]

21:41.940 --> 21:42.970
[I'm serious. I'll send you a gift later.
Remember to get the package.]

21:43.060 --> 21:43.110
[If anything's bothering you,
you can always tell me.]

21:43.140 --> 21:43.350
[My major is psychology anyway.
At least I can talk to you]

21:43.350 --> 21:43.780
[and help you get to know
more about yourself.]

21:43.810 --> 21:44.110
[What do you mean?]

21:44.130 --> 21:44.570
[You know what? Pain is a brain protest.]

21:44.860 --> 21:45.790
[To show that the line between goodwill and manipulation
is only a thin layer of candy wrapper]

21:46.040 --> 21:46.660
[There's something wrong with the candy
you gave me last month, right?]

21:47.170 --> 21:47.740
[I'll eat it properly]

21:47.760 --> 21:48.400
[I hope they can help ease your
academic stress. Don’t waste them.]

21:48.880 --> 21:49.450
[I immediately ate one.
It tasted pretty good.]

21:49.470 --> 21:49.990
[I'm glad you received it.
Do you feel better now?]

21:50.450 --> 21:50.830
[I hate you.]

21:50.850 --> 21:51.520
[Before I knew it, it was already New Year’s.
How was your day today?]

21:51.600 --> 21:53.590
Spade Q,

21:54.200 --> 21:56.200
did you kill Jason?

22:19.170 --> 22:20.000
[One payment today]

22:21.060 --> 22:22.230
[Transaction Details]

22:26.830 --> 22:28.940
[Contact] [Lin Wanxing]

22:31.030 --> 22:35.620
[Lin Wanxing]

22:36.710 --> 22:37.900
[WeChat Pay]

22:38.240 --> 22:39.390
[WeChat]

22:42.460 --> 22:42.600
[Search]

22:42.630 --> 22:43.200
[Searching Contacts]

22:43.230 --> 22:43.530
[Search]

22:43.530 --> 22:45.060
[Slack Superstar]

22:45.080 --> 22:45.450
[Add]

22:48.180 --> 22:50.110
[Send]

22:50.160 --> 22:52.380
[Sending]

22:52.910 --> 22:54.480
[Slack Superstar]

22:53.350 --> 22:54.920
Lin Wanxing.

22:56.110 --> 22:58.590
Are you Spade Q?

23:04.080 --> 23:06.160
[Hongjing No. 8 High School]

23:17.720 --> 23:19.160
I'm Ms. Sun.

23:19.830 --> 23:21.160
I heard that you

23:21.160 --> 23:23.690
are a top student
from Yongchuan University.

23:24.200 --> 23:26.510
The previous guy, Mr. Li,
didn't even know how to use a computer.

23:26.510 --> 23:28.510
The whole equipment room was a mess.

23:29.000 --> 23:31.750
It seems the equipment room
doesn't really need a computer.

23:31.750 --> 23:32.400
Here.

23:32.400 --> 23:33.790
I brought some snacks.

23:33.790 --> 23:34.750
Let's share.

23:36.030 --> 23:37.200
You're Ms. Lin, right?

23:37.200 --> 23:38.000
Try this.

23:38.110 --> 23:39.270
-Thank you.
-It's very delicious.

23:39.270 --> 23:39.920
-And this.
-Sorry.

23:39.920 --> 23:41.030
Sorry. I'm sorry.

23:41.030 --> 23:42.480
I'm late.

23:42.480 --> 23:44.080
The principal called me over

23:44.160 --> 23:46.350
to get a new notice
from the Education Bureau.

23:46.350 --> 23:47.510
Sorry for

23:47.510 --> 23:48.400
being late.

23:49.030 --> 23:50.750
Everyone, stop what you're doing.

23:50.750 --> 23:52.480
I'll read this document to you.

23:55.370 --> 23:56.610
[Agent]

23:59.270 --> 24:01.400
Notice from the Hongjing Education Bureau

24:01.400 --> 24:02.550
on Further Strengthening

24:02.550 --> 24:04.220
and Improving School Sports Work.

24:04.220 --> 24:04.980
Sorry.

24:07.240 --> 24:08.720
It's my agent calling.

24:10.030 --> 24:12.110
Put it on mute during the meeting.

24:12.110 --> 24:13.720
Just tell us directly.

24:13.720 --> 24:16.110
What exactly does this new notice say?

24:16.590 --> 24:18.000
It's mainly about Hongjing City's

24:18.000 --> 24:19.870
strong push

24:20.130 --> 24:21.330
to develop football.

24:21.720 --> 24:24.130
So this year's Youth Super League—

24:24.270 --> 24:25.160
our No. 8 High School

24:25.160 --> 24:26.350
has to take part.

24:26.350 --> 24:29.000
Haven't we been out of
the Youth Super League for years?

24:29.000 --> 24:30.350
Why are we joining now?

24:30.350 --> 24:31.960
"The all-round development of students in moral,
intellectual, and physical education."

24:31.960 --> 24:33.680
We must focus on it,

24:33.680 --> 24:34.930
especially sports.

24:34.960 --> 24:37.510
But our football team
hasn't played for 2 years.

24:37.510 --> 24:38.920
Can they do it?

24:38.920 --> 24:41.850
If we go, we'll just be eliminated
in the first round.

24:42.520 --> 24:44.200
You're selling yourselves short

24:44.200 --> 24:45.200
and giving up before even trying.

24:45.200 --> 24:46.510
Look at you!

24:47.080 --> 24:49.610
The school leaders
are very supportive of us.

24:50.160 --> 24:51.600
The principal told me repeatedly that

24:51.600 --> 24:53.840
if we have any difficulties or ideas,

24:53.920 --> 24:55.850
we should just mention them to him.

24:56.270 --> 24:58.030
But there's an important position

24:58.030 --> 25:00.480
that has to come from our P.E. department,

25:00.480 --> 25:01.790
because we are the P.E. department.

25:01.790 --> 25:03.030
The P.E. department!

25:04.240 --> 25:05.680
That is the team supervisor.

25:05.680 --> 25:06.640
Who among you

25:07.350 --> 25:08.960
will volunteer?

25:19.130 --> 25:21.230
Our track and field team has been
very busy lately. I don't have time.

25:21.230 --> 25:22.510
I don't have time.

25:24.440 --> 25:25.480
I coach basketball.

25:25.480 --> 25:26.750
What do I know about football?

25:26.750 --> 25:28.140
I can't.

25:28.620 --> 25:30.030
I don't know how to play any ball games.

25:30.030 --> 25:31.890
I only know rhythmic gymnastics.

25:33.000 --> 25:34.310
I just got here.

25:34.310 --> 25:36.970
It shouldn't have anything
to do with me, right?

25:38.110 --> 25:40.030
It seems opportunities always go
to young people

25:40.030 --> 25:42.790
who dare to think and take action.

25:43.240 --> 25:44.200
Ms. Lin.

25:44.720 --> 25:48.350
Your chance to shine has finally arrived.

25:49.260 --> 25:50.110
Look.

25:50.590 --> 25:52.500
This is the newly drafted

25:52.520 --> 25:54.680
-No way.
-list of the football team members.

25:54.680 --> 25:55.830
Please review it.

25:55.850 --> 25:57.920
This glorious and challenging task

25:57.950 --> 25:59.350
will be entrusted to you.

26:03.110 --> 26:04.240
Me?

26:05.350 --> 26:06.200
Let's go eat.

26:06.200 --> 26:07.110
Bye.

26:08.550 --> 26:09.310
Dir—

26:09.920 --> 26:12.780
Director Qian,
you did this on purpose, didn't you?

26:18.000 --> 26:19.720
Playing dumb?

26:19.720 --> 26:21.270
Pretending not to see me?

26:24.540 --> 26:26.640
[Crossword Puzzle]

26:24.610 --> 26:25.610
"Family Line..."

26:28.350 --> 26:29.750
"Family Line Dying Out"?

26:31.400 --> 26:32.600
You haven't left yet?

26:32.760 --> 26:35.000
You have a good mindset.

26:35.590 --> 26:36.510
Do you need me for something?

26:36.510 --> 26:37.710
Come on, grab a chair.

26:37.770 --> 26:38.430
Have a seat.

26:47.200 --> 26:48.320
Director Qian.

26:48.430 --> 26:50.820
I majored in psychology.

26:53.210 --> 26:55.140
Everyone has their own specialty.

26:56.160 --> 26:57.290
Well...

26:59.930 --> 27:01.970
Since you're so good at psychology,

27:02.070 --> 27:03.480
I think you're the perfect person

27:03.480 --> 27:05.110
to lead the team.

27:05.140 --> 27:06.910
It's completely outside my field.

27:06.910 --> 27:09.240
Actually, you don't need to worry so much.

27:09.240 --> 27:10.570
Let me tell you a secret.

27:10.750 --> 27:13.400
Actually, No. 8 High School's
football team is pretty strong.

27:13.400 --> 27:14.480
When they were in junior high,

27:14.480 --> 27:15.480
they even won

27:15.480 --> 27:17.080
the city championship once.

27:17.160 --> 27:19.510
Really?

27:19.680 --> 27:21.280
Really. I'm not lying to you.

27:21.710 --> 27:23.420
Let me show you these kids.

27:22.530 --> 27:24.860
[Hongjing No. 8 High School
Football Team Roster]

27:23.490 --> 27:24.250
Look.

27:25.070 --> 27:26.600
They are all full of energy.

27:27.240 --> 27:29.200
Smart and ambitious.

27:27.520 --> 27:29.360
[Name: Qin Ao] [Name: Lin Lu]
[Name: Qi Liang]

27:29.520 --> 27:31.240
And you say you're not lying?

27:32.070 --> 27:33.240
Come on, Young Master!

27:33.240 --> 27:35.440
-I've been so loyal to you!
-Beautiful.

27:35.440 --> 27:36.070
What is it?

27:37.790 --> 27:38.920
Honest.

27:38.920 --> 27:40.720
I'm a senior in Class 5.
My name is Qin Ao.

27:40.720 --> 27:41.920
Qin as in Emperor Qin.

27:41.920 --> 27:43.570
Ao as in Tibetan Mastiff,
without the "dog" component.

27:43.570 --> 27:44.680
Disciplined.

27:44.710 --> 27:46.690
That boy has been playing football
there all afternoon.

27:46.690 --> 27:48.150
He must be skipping class.

27:49.310 --> 27:50.880
They're highly skilled

27:50.880 --> 27:52.400
and very competitive.

27:52.790 --> 27:53.750
Director Qian,

27:54.560 --> 27:56.200
my abilities are limited.

27:56.400 --> 27:58.460
I can't take on this responsibility.

27:58.590 --> 27:59.650
I think

27:59.920 --> 28:01.580
you should find someone else.

28:02.640 --> 28:04.600
You're still on probation.

28:04.630 --> 28:07.000
If you fail
to meet the school's expectations,

28:07.000 --> 28:07.590
let me tell you,

28:07.590 --> 28:09.460
many people around you,

28:09.510 --> 28:10.440
including me,

28:10.440 --> 28:11.440
won't be able to help you.

28:11.440 --> 28:13.830
Just treat it as taking the kids out

28:14.310 --> 28:16.400
for some outdoor exercise.

28:16.450 --> 28:18.570
Actually, the results don't matter.

28:21.440 --> 28:23.370
Winning or losing doesn't matter?

28:25.550 --> 28:26.430
It's just that

28:26.450 --> 28:29.380
there's not much time left
before the match.

28:29.750 --> 28:31.070
It's this Sunday.

28:31.720 --> 28:32.640
Don't worry.

28:32.640 --> 28:35.000
The school leaders have always been

28:35.000 --> 28:37.240
very supportive and helpful
to young teachers.

28:37.240 --> 28:38.100
How about this?

28:38.200 --> 28:39.400
Tomorrow afternoon,

28:39.480 --> 28:40.750
we will

28:41.270 --> 28:43.200
meet these kids on the football team

28:43.200 --> 28:44.240
formally.

28:44.640 --> 28:45.830
Tomorrow?

28:45.830 --> 28:47.760
I've already sent out the notices.

28:49.110 --> 28:50.290
Really.

28:51.920 --> 28:53.610
But there's no getting out

28:53.640 --> 28:55.160
of this job.

28:55.480 --> 28:56.270
Good luck.

29:10.070 --> 29:11.310
So many notices?

29:11.490 --> 29:11.890
[Contacts]

29:13.290 --> 29:14.570
[I'm Winfred]

29:15.070 --> 29:16.920
Winfred?

29:17.590 --> 29:18.960
Who is this?

29:18.220 --> 29:19.150
[Added by searching your phone number]

29:21.540 --> 29:21.800
[Recents]

29:21.820 --> 29:22.290
[Agent]

29:23.440 --> 29:27.750
The number you dialed is busy.
Please try again later.

29:28.330 --> 29:29.120
[Creamy Taro Milk Tea with Pudding]

29:29.010 --> 29:31.160
Let me order a cup of milk tea
to calm my nerves.

29:29.140 --> 29:30.210
[Brown Sugar Boba Milk Tea]

29:33.310 --> 29:34.750
Behind this tree.

29:35.310 --> 29:36.000
Behind the tree.

29:36.000 --> 29:37.270
Listen to the footsteps.

29:37.270 --> 29:39.000
-Reload Reload first.
-I'm out of ammo.

29:39.000 --> 29:40.480
Reload first.
Your high-powered scope won't work.

29:40.480 --> 29:41.200
Switch to a low-powered scope!

29:41.200 --> 29:42.160
Isn't there a low-powered scope here?

29:42.160 --> 29:44.360
I don't have a high-powered scope, bro.

29:45.000 --> 29:46.330
His teammate will be here in a sec.

29:46.330 --> 29:47.940
You should run first.

29:48.480 --> 29:49.790
This way. This way.

29:49.790 --> 29:51.390
-Hello, teacher.
-This way!

29:54.720 --> 29:55.510
What are you doing?

29:55.510 --> 29:56.270
Studying.

29:56.270 --> 29:57.200
Relaxing.

29:58.220 --> 29:58.830
[Qin Ao, Former Football Team Forward]

29:58.850 --> 29:59.700
[Lin Lu, Former Football Team Defender]

29:59.730 --> 30:01.010
[Qi Liang, Former Football Team Defender]

30:00.000 --> 30:00.750
Right.

30:02.030 --> 30:04.030
What are their names?

30:04.030 --> 30:05.510
Do you think I'm stupid?

30:05.510 --> 30:07.550
Like I'd tell you their names
are Lin Lu and Qi Liang,

30:07.550 --> 30:08.960
and then let you go tell Jin Laoyao

30:08.960 --> 30:10.790
that we're skipping class
to play games here?

30:10.790 --> 30:12.200
Lin Lu? Qi Liang?

30:10.890 --> 30:12.330
[Name: Qin Ao] [Name: Lin Lu]
[Name: Qi Liang]

30:12.200 --> 30:13.920
-Boss!
-Come on, bro.

30:14.400 --> 30:15.200
What's wrong?

30:15.400 --> 30:16.400
Our names...

30:18.720 --> 30:19.920
Lin Lu.

30:19.920 --> 30:21.920
How good are you guys at playing football?

30:21.920 --> 30:23.240
I'm awesome at it.

30:23.240 --> 30:24.550
Qi Liang is also great.

30:24.550 --> 30:27.000
We used to be on the school football team.

30:29.030 --> 30:30.000
What about your boss?

30:30.000 --> 30:30.790
How does he play?

30:30.790 --> 30:31.680
Him?

30:31.680 --> 30:32.550
He sucks.

30:32.790 --> 30:33.640
Lin Lu.

30:34.920 --> 30:36.320
What are you laughing at?

30:36.720 --> 30:38.520
You are indeed just average.

30:39.750 --> 30:42.200
Since you were
on the school football team,

30:42.680 --> 30:44.030
why aren't you playing anymore?

30:44.030 --> 30:45.440
What year is this?

30:45.440 --> 30:46.640
Football is outdated.

30:46.640 --> 30:48.400
It's the era of e-sports now.

30:52.590 --> 30:53.830
You three,

30:53.830 --> 30:54.760
wait for me here.

30:56.240 --> 30:57.750
Why did you have to say

30:57.750 --> 30:58.510
my name?

30:58.510 --> 30:59.640
-Who sucks at football?
-Why were you so loud?

30:59.640 --> 31:00.640
-Say it again.
-Why?

31:00.640 --> 31:01.270
Who sucks at football?

31:01.270 --> 31:01.960
Didn't you say it first?

31:01.960 --> 31:03.030
-Right?
-Who sucks at football?

31:03.030 --> 31:04.240
Why did you say our names?

31:04.240 --> 31:05.520
-Yeah.
-So what if I did?

31:05.520 --> 31:07.120
You just had to say our names?

31:08.550 --> 31:09.400
Let's go!

31:09.400 --> 31:12.330
-The teacher will be back soon.
-Where are you going?

31:14.570 --> 31:15.270
Teacher,

31:15.270 --> 31:18.330
ordering takeout at school
violates the school rules.

31:18.920 --> 31:20.030
I am a teacher.

31:21.510 --> 31:22.070
Then...

31:22.070 --> 31:23.720
Then you can do it.

31:24.720 --> 31:27.510
Director Qian said
your team used to be very strong

31:27.510 --> 31:29.550
and even won some championships.

31:29.920 --> 31:31.270
Why did you give up?

31:35.000 --> 31:36.000
Boss. Boss. Boss.

31:46.550 --> 31:47.440
Teacher!

31:48.750 --> 31:50.550
We didn't win the championship.

31:50.680 --> 31:51.790
We'll always be...

31:53.240 --> 31:54.000
runners-up.

31:55.440 --> 31:57.200
Why bring that up? Let's go.

32:03.110 --> 32:04.440
What's wrong with them?

32:31.610 --> 32:32.370
Hello?

32:32.390 --> 32:33.030
Ms. Lin.

32:33.060 --> 32:34.320
Here's the situation.

32:34.440 --> 32:35.750
The previous tenant on the 3rd floor

32:35.750 --> 32:36.590
had a minor change of plans.

32:36.590 --> 32:37.720
They said they're not renting anymore.

32:37.720 --> 32:38.920
What?

32:38.920 --> 32:40.720
Didn't they already move in yesterday?

32:40.720 --> 32:41.750
A mother and son?

32:42.000 --> 32:43.680
Yes, the mother and son from before.

32:43.680 --> 32:45.210
They've already moved out.

32:45.830 --> 32:46.550
Well...

32:46.720 --> 32:48.070
does that count as a breach of contract?

32:48.070 --> 32:48.920
Don't worry.

32:48.920 --> 32:51.000
I've already found you a new tenant.

32:51.000 --> 32:53.110
The rent is double the original amount.

32:53.110 --> 32:54.570
Thanks for your hard work.

32:54.880 --> 32:56.240
It's nothing.

32:56.960 --> 32:59.030
It's just that the new tenant has...

32:59.030 --> 33:00.640
a tiny request.

33:00.950 --> 33:02.120
What is it?

33:02.140 --> 33:03.180
Well...

33:03.240 --> 33:04.110
He needs a bathtub.

33:04.110 --> 33:05.070
A bathtub?

33:05.750 --> 33:08.200
How can a bathtub
be installed in my apartment?

33:08.200 --> 33:09.750
The bathtub has already arrived.

33:09.750 --> 33:11.680
The workers are installing it now.

33:11.720 --> 33:12.590
What?

33:13.270 --> 33:14.530
Wait for me to get back.

33:28.270 --> 33:28.750
Here.

33:29.750 --> 33:30.550
Ms. Lin.

33:30.920 --> 33:31.720
1,100.

33:33.920 --> 33:34.720
Ms. Lin.

33:36.530 --> 33:38.440
This bathtub is imported from Italy.

33:38.440 --> 33:39.700
Looks premium, right?

33:39.910 --> 33:40.810
Don't worry.

33:41.000 --> 33:42.070
The tenant paid

33:42.070 --> 33:43.960
for the installation of this bathtub.

33:43.960 --> 33:45.970
This is a good thing for us.

33:46.160 --> 33:47.480
Ms. Lin.

33:47.480 --> 33:49.310
This tenant is very sincere.

33:49.310 --> 33:52.000
You know, the market competition
is fierce now.

33:52.000 --> 33:54.200
Your apartment wouldn't rent out at all.

33:54.200 --> 33:56.160
But you shouldn't have done it
without telling me.

33:56.160 --> 33:57.070
What if this bathtub leaks

33:57.070 --> 33:58.670
and the water gets into my room?

33:58.670 --> 34:00.440
I called you this morning.

34:00.440 --> 34:01.480
You never answered.

34:01.480 --> 34:03.520
The tenant was in a hurry

34:03.750 --> 34:04.920
and willing to pay more.

34:04.920 --> 34:06.270
So I agreed first.

34:06.270 --> 34:07.440
It's almost 6 PM.

34:07.440 --> 34:08.239
I'm in a bit of a rush.

34:08.239 --> 34:09.350
So I'll get going now.

34:09.350 --> 34:10.070
Ms. Lin,

34:10.070 --> 34:11.639
let's keep in touch!

34:15.110 --> 34:17.400
Who exactly is the landlord here?

34:24.630 --> 34:26.429
Where did this weirdo come from?

34:27.000 --> 34:29.000
If he can afford an imported bathtub,

34:29.000 --> 34:30.800
why rent my apartment?

34:54.750 --> 34:55.790
Hello, Ms. Lin.

34:57.880 --> 34:59.230
The QR Code?

35:01.630 --> 35:02.960
I am your new tenant,

35:06.060 --> 35:06.830
Wang Fa.

35:24.860 --> 35:26.540
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

35:27.480 --> 35:28.970
♪ Because you're with me ♪

35:31.710 --> 35:33.240
♪ The light shimmers ♪

35:34.500 --> 35:35.660
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

35:37.430 --> 35:38.500
♪ Running towards you ♪

35:39.370 --> 35:40.630
♪ I keep moving fearlessly ♪

35:44.400 --> 35:45.560
♪ Walk side by side ♪

35:46.180 --> 35:48.310
♪ Become ourselves ♪
